{"tid":2217883,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"星期六 我想摺 日日摺","createTime":"2020-09-25T18:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T05:59:06.000Z","uid":359022,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6cbea77d6b09de2654d6a50ce1ca8188d0809daf","tid":2217883,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T18:59:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1644407/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1644407/page/1</a><br />\n唔知大家仲記唔記得舊年有個摺連豬摺紙鶴活動？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REJmxwA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREJmxwA.jpg&h=e606b4fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大人細路一齊折，一齊I wish 我想 香港點樣<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻或者每時每刻我最想就係12港人可以儘快番黎香港，可以同家人見面。<br />\n<br />\n我想摺連豬，亦希望大家可以記得舊年嘅呢個活動&mdash;覺得鬱悶嘅時候，放空一下、隨手拎張紙，摺隻豬摺隻鶴或飛機或飛鏢，日日摺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望佢地番黎嘅時候，我地可以將呢段日子嘅祝福送到佢地手上，有一大堆連豬連狗迎接大家。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望呢堆摺紙可以成為微少嘅動力，又或者少少安慰，聚集成實物、看得見嘅盼望。<br />\n<br />\n細佬獻醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />曬紅連登豬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0jwCQmV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jwCQmV.jpg&h=bd0f2a45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登豬摺紙教學 Credits to 呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1644407/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1644407/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gtdxEfC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgtdxEfC.jpg&h=59ae9226&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e3de67fe40793bc7c90a10b10646491e7248952","tid":2217883,"uid":62305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T19:09:23.000Z","msg":"咁你都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d25a8f81cc3b93f5fa76ec973347fec5135928","tid":2217883,"uid":219969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T19:11:44.000Z","msg":"憑豬寄意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaeb7eb5fa8d7e7f0033f38e6a8577290c1cb9c8","tid":2217883,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e3de67fe40793bc7c90a10b10646491e7248952","tid":2217883,"uid":62305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T19:09:23.000Z","msg":"咁你都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T19:13:08.000Z","msg":"一齊摺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎大家po上黎<br />\n拉得太緊 偶爾都需要另類方式放鬆下 而又唔覺得放鬆就係罪"},{"pid":"03f5be79c31480c2e3b32f7d2de3ed750bf2511f","tid":2217883,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19d25a8f81cc3b93f5fa76ec973347fec5135928","tid":2217883,"uid":219969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T19:11:44.000Z","msg":"憑豬寄意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T19:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好名好名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />標題L"},{"pid":"38c38524562e4ac1a35954412c4b371a1bcaf019","tid":2217883,"uid":103965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T19:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"